      "title": "My latest  cartoon for Guardian Books",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s640x960/d7b77f3877f09e38e2ae02f208e33d888d93566b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"791\" data-orig-width=\"1448\" alt=\"Two hooded figures with lamps approach a moonlit, isolated cottage. A woman answers the door. We have come for the child, says the hooded figure So soon? she asks It is time, says the hooded figure. The woman is distraught. We should never have got him a library card! What is done cannot be undone, says the hooded figure We couldn&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;t see the harm! We just wanted him to enjoy reading!  For most, it ends there, says the hooded figure, turning away and walking into the wilderness Oh lord, What have I done! says the woman, the child walks past her and out into the darkness with them. Do not cry mother.  I am a writer now.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s75x75_c1/b686bc3be033d35cad9f5ed56c6541231574d5c9.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s100x200/b938d98e22bc45583ab0e956cb95ba742b08ce26.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s250x400/fc8e2ccd54fda98b5decc0907e09bc51cffede91.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s400x600/58f466c074fc6ed1608043f2124adc5d73cc995a.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s500x750/e0c00f3c5ac1a183888ebded453ff10048662f74.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s540x810/39f2ed7f19d27412e14d9f0ee3df7e4cc9ebdc90.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s640x960/d7b77f3877f09e38e2ae02f208e33d888d93566b.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a1cc642ae8ecfe9c3c32e473a3415bde/a26b3edd27567f94-9d/s1280x1920/ea05f2e833427875cc709593b7ecd401c843b9da.