      "title": "A recent New Scientist cartoon ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s640x960/70369e46aca12f59a12338ff8e4f8336c8d1166c.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"865\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Two archaeologists stand in a trench looking at an unearthed, fossilised, time machine and a tyrannosaurus skull in whose jaws is a human skeleton holding an aerosol can. One says: &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;These fossils would appear to suggest that, while Professor Cooper's time machine was a great success, his dinosaur repellent formula was not.&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s75x75_c1/cd4e1a8934c4bb84e288ea44ff0b8e3fa9ca39a7.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s100x200/e3f7cad6d3f0038023b76bdb73b17397fc4a4780.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s250x400/f1d8a97fc29d529ea25a96d210c3a4c41d7fd64d.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s400x600/ded875beff4937989d48dfcd16558037ae220940.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s500x750/3ba744ac81a9a19275cd74db7dda2dcfab08b01d.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s540x810/44d3e4d8011e19a47731cbce70f0c0a4d21f1494.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s640x960/70369e46aca12f59a12338ff8e4f8336c8d1166c.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9c616fd7295adeeefd2ab51521d238fb/c589960cbd1082e0-99/s1280x1920/50b294bc32c1c1210e3731ea8854951e6f00cdc4.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
